name: Vintage Suitcase Set
description:
A set of 3 beautiful mini suitcases in vintage style floral patterns. Perfect for hiding away bits and bobs or as adorable carry cases for children.
The cases are really sturdily made from strong cardboard with decorative stitching and finished to a high standard.
They feature bronze coloured fastenings, faux leather straps and the interior is decorated in grey florals.
The cases measure:
29 by 20 by 9.5cm
23 by 17 by 8.5cm
21 by 10 by 8cm

name: Animal Ring Tidy
description:
These adorable ring holders are available in a choice of four animal designs, each with a sweet, subtly detailed face. A lovely addition to any dressing table, the dish at the base can also be used for earrings.
Each one measures approximately 7cm tall and 6.5cm wide at the base. These come boxed and are ideal stocking fillers or secret santa gifts!

name: Butterfly Frame
description:
A cream painted metal frame with distressed edges for the perfect shabby chic finish. The cut-out mounted butterflies are ever so pretty.
The overall size of the frame measures 6 inches tall by 4 inches wide and  holds a 3 by 2 inch photo. With portrait stand on the back.

name: Gentleman Mug
description:
Feel like a dapper Dan whilst drinking your morning cup of coffee with these quirky moustache mugs. Featuring a tweed textured print for the proper gentleman! 
Each mug measures 9cm tall by 7.5cm in diameter (not including handle)

Only one 'Square Glasses' design left in stock.

name: Large Floral Heart
description:
Beautiful metal hearts in a choice of pretty floral designs. These are impressively large and make an attractive addition to any home.
Hand finished with distressed gold edging for a shabby chic look. 
Each heart measures 17cm tall, 13cm wide and is lovely and plump!

As a handmade item please allow for variations in the design.
The 'Strawberry' design is currently unavailable.

name: Plaque Frame
description:
A beautiful wooden photo frame in the style of a vintage door plate. The raised ornate design features distressed edges for the perfect shabby chic finish. In a choice of dusky pink or buttery cream.
The overall size of the frame measures 8 inches tall by 3 inches wide and  holds a 3 by 2 inch photo. With portrait stand on the back.

name: Owl Suitcase Set

29 by 20 by 9.5cm

21 by 10 by 8cm

name: Woodpecker Scarf
description:
A lovely item from our quality range of scarves featuring a beautiful woodpecker print in a shade of denim blue.
For an idea of scale, the woodpecker measures approximately 40cm tall.
A scarf always makes a well received gift! Make sure you view our full range.
The scarf measures 180cm by 110cm and can double as a wrap or sarong. Hand wash with care.

name: Polka Dot Case
description:
An infinitely useful pouch in a choice of four colours.
The outer is made from Japanese polka dot linen, which has a pre-aged, vintage look, and trimmed with cream cotton lace.
With zip fastening and practical waterproof lining.
20cm wide by 12cm tall.
Please allow for slight variations in the fabric colour/texture.

Last chance to buy!

name: Ditsy Floral Suitcases
description:
A set of 3 beautiful mini suitcases in vintage shades of pink, brown and blue ditsy florals.
Perfect for hiding away bits and bobs or as adorable carry cases for children.
The cases are really sturdily made from strong cardboard with decorative stitching and finished to a high standard.
They feature bronze coloured fastenings and faux leather straps.
The interior is decorated in grey florals.
The cases measure:
29 by 20 by 9.5cm
23 by 17 by 8.5cm
21 by 10 by 8cm

name: Enamel Heart Board
description:
This large metal heart has been finished with a beautiful enamel coating on both sides, like a pretty seashell! Ideal for displaying notes and photos, the board also makes a lovely piece of wall art when left bare.
Each board is sold with 3 button magnets in co-ordinating colours.
The heart measures an impressive 42cm wide and 42cm tall. Hangs from a long & strong white rope.

Purple is now sold out.

name: Ornate Multi Frame
description:
A vintage twist on the modern multi frame: Four French-inspired ornate frames join together to make one large frame in a buttery shade of  cream with distressed, shabby chic finish.
Free standing with support arm on the back.
The apertures take photos measuring 3 x 3 inches, 2.5 x 3.5 inches and two at 3.5 x 5 inches.
The overall size of the frame is approximately 30cm by 29cm.

name: Button Heart
description:
These beautiful button hearts are truly original. No two are the same!
Dozens of colourful, opalescent buttons have been set in white resin to create a striking piece of home decor. 
The heart measures an impressive 15cm long, 11cm at the widest and a plump 2.5cm deep. Hangs from a white satin ribbon.
Each heart is hand finished so please allow for variations and irregularities.

name: Vintage Bottles
description:
Add a touch of vintage charm to your shelves with these lovely bottles, available in a choice of two designs. The glass has been styled to look vintage, complete with wibbles and imperfections.
With the ceramic lid and air-tight seal, these bottles are as practical as they are pretty. They would make an excellent gift, empty or filled with a treat (flavoured oils, compotes, liquor etc) 
Each bottle measures 15cm tall and 6cm in diameter at the base. Priced at £4.50 each or £8 a pair (one of each design)

name: Mini Floral Heart
description:
Sweet mini metal hearts decorated with an assortment of ditsy floral patterns. Hand finished with distressed gold edging for a shabby chic look. 
Each heart measures 6cm tall by 5cm wide.
The designs are lettered to help with ordering.

These hearts are produced on a fair trade basis by skilled artisans in India. As a handmade item please allow for variations in the design.

name: Floral Tea Tray
description:
A pretty floral tray made from sturdy, hardwearing plastic.
Infinitely useful for tidying up around the home, not just afternoon tea!
The tray measures 21cm long, 14cm wide and 1.5cm tall.

name: Butterfly Magnet Set
description:
A set of four glass magnets with detailed butterfly designs.
Pretty and practical! A lovely gift.
Each magnet measures 3cm in diameter.

name: 12 Red Heart Pegs
description:
Adorable mini wooden pegs with a folksy heart attached.
So very versatile: use them in scrapbooks, to display cards, with gift tags, leaving notes or keeping open packets fresh.
Of course they'd also be a lovely way to display Christmas cards.
You will receive a set of 12 pegs and each peg measures 3cm long.

name: Classic Car Scarf
description:
A lovely item from our quality range of scarves featuring a quirky car print. 
The scarf itself is a beigey-caramel with grey, gold and plum cars. For an idea of scale, the plum car measures 7.5cm long.
A scarf always makes a well received gift! Make sure you view our full range.
The scarf measures 180cm by 110cm and can double as a wrap or sarong. Hand wash with care.

name: Nordic Hearts
description:
Add a touch of Scandinavian chic to your home with these lovely wooden folk hearts.
Each heart measures 8cm wide, 7.5cm tall and 1cm thick.
Available to buy individually or as a pair and save 50p!

name: Wooden Fish Garland
description:
A nautical garland featuring 3 sweet wooden fishies in stripes and polka dots. The rustic twine is strung with faux pearls.
From top to bottom the overall length is 40cm. Each fishy is 4cm at the widest.

name: Mr Bird Scarf
description:
These birdies have places to go, people to see! They're all dressed up in  bow ties, looking quite the dapper critters.
The scarf is a bluey shade of grey with abstract bird illustrations in hot pink. The birds measure an average 8cm tall.
A scarf always makes a well received gift! Make sure you view our full range.
The scarf measures 180cm by 110cm and can double as a wrap or sarong. Hand wash with care.

name: Wing Trinket Box
description:
A heart shaped trinket box with beautifully detailed feathers, cast from off-white resin.
The box measures 8.5cm at the widest and longest and 4cm tall.

name: Hydrangea Hook
description:
Make a statement with this beautiful shabby chic wall hook, featuring a large hydrangea finished in chalk white with distressed silver highlights.
The hook measures 18cm wide, 23cm tall and 7cm deep.
An impressive size and beautifully decorative for a functional piece.

Last chance to buy!

name: Monogram Cushion
description:
What could be nicer than a custom made gift?
Or a personalised finishing touch for your home?

My cushions are a cute, modern take on the traditional monogram.
Each letter is made from dozens of new and vintage buttons and sewn with matching thread.
I work on a variety of fabrics, plain and patterned, and no two cushions are ever the same!

This is a listing for your custom designed cushion. Please message me with your design ideas.
The photos here are some of my completed creations that are now in loving homes.

£27 is the standard price for a 16 inch square patterned fabric cushion decorated with 100g of buttons and a plump inner pad.
For a plain fabric cushion the price is £25.

name: Tropical Fish Scarf
description:
A lovely item from our quality range of scarves. 
The scarf features mountain ranges, underwater plants and shoals of brightly coloured fish. 
A scarf always makes a well received gift! Make sure you view our full range. 
The scarf measures 180cm by 110cm and can double as a wrap or sarong. Hand wash with care.

name: Caterpillar Bunting
description: An absolute children's classic, The Very Hungry Caterpillar has sold a copy a minute since 1969! This handmade bunting is enormous fun, perfect for children's bedrooms and the young at heart! The flags are sewn from official Hungry Caterpillar cotton with green polka dot backs and finished with neat top stitching. Each flag measures approximately 10cm tall. The mini size is perfect for draping across shelves or above a bed. Each string measures approximately 1 meter long and features 7 flags. This bunting is made to order so please allow 1-2 weeks for creation & delivery.

name: Rose Paper Tape
description:
This lovely set vintage style paper tapes comes in three gorgeous designs: a plummy plaid, pinky-red doily and pale turquoise roses. 
So pretty, perfect for scrap booking, crafting, gift wrapping or jazzing up your notebooks!
The rolls of tape measure 1cm, 1.5cm and 2cm wide by at least 5 metres long.

You will receive all three tapes.

name: Ceramic Bunting
description:
A sweet decorative item for your home that looks lovely hung along the front of a shelf, across a mantel or anywhere you please!
These could also be used as a finishing touch on a special gift.
Each string of 'Love' bunting measures 37cm in total width, with the 'Me & You' design measuring 48cm.
The ceramic pennants measure 6.5cm tall.

As a handmade item, please allow for variations in the design.

name: Rose Butterflies
description:
A pair of butterfly clips in gorgeous shades of dusky rose.
The clip back makes these so versatile: 
In flower arrangements, on gifts, photo holders, on curtains, as place holders, in party bags or even as hair clips!
The wings are made from feathers with painted glitter detail.
Each butterfly has an 8cm wing span.

Just £2.50 postage on as many butterflies as you purchase!
Butterflies are sold in pairs.

name: Skull Bunting
description:
Ahoy me hearties! This skull and crossbones bunting is perfect for any pirate's home, garden or party!
The bunting pennants are made from cotton, double sided and finished to a high standard.
Each string of bunting measures 320cm long with 8 pennants.
Each pennant measures 24cm wide by 28cm tall.

name: Twelve Scarves
description:
A lovely range of quality scarves, brand new to Dear Blackbird!
With 12 designs to choose from, you can never have too many scarves and they always make a well received gift.

Each scarf is lettered to help with ordering.
A, E & K - 175cm by 100cm. Also ideal as a sarong.
B, I & L - 170cm by 50cm. Intricately woven fabric.
C, D & H - 175cm by 60cm. With lace tassels.
F, G & J - 170cm by 55cm. Lightweight soft fabric with fringing.

description:

These felt bunny brooches are just about the cutest thing we've ever seen! 
A red ribbon is tied around their neck with a tiny, functional bell that tinkles so prettily.
Backed in red felt with a secure brooch pin.
Each bunny measures approximately 7cm tall by 6.5cm wide.
As these brooches are all hand made, please allow for slight variations.

The colours are lettered for easy ordering.
Last chance to buy!

name: Tea Light Holder
description:
A very pretty tea light holder decorated with the classic sentiment 'home sweet home.' Made from glass with a printed design and available in a choice of four colours.

It's all part of the charm!

Save 50% on original selling price.

Each heart measures 12cm tall, 11cm wide and 1cm thick.
These are hand painted so please allow for variations and imperfections. It's all part of the shabby chic charm!

Save over 25% on original selling price.

description:

Each metal hook is hand finished with decoupage and gold edging for a distinctly shabby chic look.
These look lovely grouped together or as an individual accent piece.
Whilst the hook is fairly strong, please don't overload it!
The hook measures 7.5cm at the widest by 13cm tall. 
With keyhole  mount on the back of the heart. 
The designs are lettered for ease of ordering.

Save over 25% on original selling price.

With an airtight seal to keep food fresh, perfect for snacks, packed lunches or leftovers.
They can of course be used outside of the kitchen, just to keep bits and pieces tidy.
The tubs measure:
Small - 3 inch diameter, 1.5 inches tall
Medium - 3.5 inch diameter, 1.75 inches tall
Large - 4.25 inch diameter, 2 inches tall
BPA free, dishwasher safe and microwavable between -20° & +120°

Now on sale! Save 40% on original selling price.

Featuring a hardback fabric cover decorated allover with small bicycles.
The notebook measures 15cm by 11cm, has lined pages and a co-ordinating elastic closure.

Now on sale! Save 40% on original selling price.

These lovely hanging photo frames make such a pretty decor piece. The frame comes in a choice of two pretty prints, both with intricate wooden lace trim. With distressed edges for the perfect shabby chic finish.

Painted in weathered blue and hangs from simple rustic twine.
The heart measures 15.5cm tall, 0.5cm thick and 6cm at the widest.

These gorgeous glass tea light holders are just the thing to perk up grey days. With gold beaded trim and speckled metallic paint, which allows the light to flicker so prettily.
Each holder measures 8cm tall by 7cm wide.

Sold in sets of 3 tea light holders of the same colour.

These beautiful, Scandinavian style Christmas decorations feature pretty red gingham ribbon and that authentic sleigh bell sound.
The star garland measures 22cm long and features patterned bells which measure 2cm wide.
The circle garland measures 22cm long with 2.5cm bells.

This bell is produced on a fair trade basis in India. As a handmade item please allow for variations in the design.
